{"tid":1495391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【我宣布】中秋開始罷工罷到支爆為止","createTime":"2019-08-22T04:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T15:17:26.000Z","uid":300554,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5e898013448f622116ad8e34da9dbd34d390b28c","tid":1495391,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:55:23.000Z","msg":"又話要推爆行動post，成個熱門都無人講！？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>升級罷工，刻不容緩！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n與其晚晚瞓唔著睇住live擔心又有勇武犧牲，<br />\n不如自發升級以持續連續延續的罷工去保護大家啦！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">八五罷一日，政府都只係一聲冷笑<br />\n九二再罷一日，政府就更加大大力恥笑！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人講到咁口響話光復香港，一諗到無咗份工就集體縮沙，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">港共一早睇死你啦！</span></span></strong>除咗班勇武我地依班打工仔有徹底爭取五大訴求咩？92出完黎咪又係繼續俾警黑恰上心口，啲狗繼續狠手打手足打到斷骨盲眼，被捕被劈嘅數字每日遞增⋯ 你忍心咩？！甘心咩！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/msQ2KYS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmsQ2KYS.jpg&h=dd7d4001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好，唔好話六月以嚟政府做咗幾多衰野，<br />\n淨係睇番依22年嚟香港平民百姓點過先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzLeA6y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzLeA6y.jpg&h=cd3d1c66&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BZ7bET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BZ7bET.jpg&h=64df5747&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNECyTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNECyTe.jpg&h=b8ea2cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1w10yf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1w10yf.jpg&h=d10abbc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2fx7d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2fx7d2.jpg&h=3eb83fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Mo0wFH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Mo0wFH.jpg&h=50cd2e28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYckwFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYckwFJ.jpg&h=0664b67e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府咁多年嚟有當過我地係人咩？沉默就被人當契弟！俾人呃足22年，香港人的脊椎生出來「無力感」再的長不出「骨氣」任，法治失衡，暴政橫行，貧富懸殊，新聞被蠶食，言論自由逐漸喪失⋯ 林鄭仲叫大家靜待經濟穩定，靜下來讓社會和諧？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2juOFzW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2juOFzW.jpg&h=7b395707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從一開始佢個屎忽鬼！佢話我哋收錢出嚟行，我哋就要話佢知香港人良心並不廉價！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">保住良心，食少兩餐，在所不惜！</span><br />\n    <br />\n<em>若你唔想香港繼續各區硝煙彌漫催淚放題；<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5uGQ5yL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5uGQ5yL.jpg&h=8c33e65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n若你唔想香港變成大灣區香港市；<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i9tzNNp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi9tzNNp.jpg&h=f66bed9c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JmLVxd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJmLVxd6.jpg&h=8d3e81ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n若你唔想廿年後佢仲要打喱場仗；</em><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0ZWgFP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0ZWgFP.jpg&h=69fbe74c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDyjYUb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDyjYUb.jpg&h=739ca55e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你要明白依場革命致勝之道乃<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇和大合體！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBqx7Bs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBqx7Bs.jpg&h=b87be7cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全香港人團結起來決一死戰，啟動持續罷工就係最後武器！<br />\n喺大家儲足SP終於要發動嘅終極地圖砲！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9月2號</span>全民大三罷</strong></ins>，打工仔不要讓罷課嘅學生孤單<br />\n人人成為人肉文宣，每個打工仔都去號召更多打工仔：<br />\n<strong>一齊<span style=\"color: red;\">續罷48小時</span>以上</strong>，若然個屎忽鬼依然唔回應，我哋一於再升級！<br />\n-＞<ins><strong>由<span style=\"color: red;\">9月13號中秋</span>開始發動終極地圖砲，一齊罷工罷到<span style=\"color: red;\">10月1號國難日</span>！！  </strong></ins><br />\n=&gt; 用香港人嘅骨氣，賀佢個國難，預祝佢支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n信我，地圖砲一旦發動，好快，我哋就會睇到一個煥然一新嘅美麗新香港。<br />\n記住，唔係中國香港，係屬於自由世界嘅，香港。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />I will recap again in Chinese:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>9月2號全民大三罷文宣日</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n話畀你老友知、話畀你男友知、話畀你老婆知、話畀你隔離個BB知，我地要持續罷！<br />\n政府若然態度依舊我地就啟動地圖砲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>9.13終極地圖砲啟動，全民大罷工至10.1</ins></span></strong></span> <br />\n記住，9.2同我大大聲傳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「我宣布9.13全民大罷工至10.1！」</span></span></strong><br />\n國慶吖嗱！支爆就有你份啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港共仲唔冚家剷！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d629cd6045b1758e0feaa5367877399f2fa2f6e","tid":1495391,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟我講！！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我宣布9.13全民大罷工至10.1！」</span></strong>"},{"pid":"32c939ca856fb2d5c390f491ce930c10cf61c748","tid":1495391,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟我講！！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我宣布9.13全民大罷工至10.1！」</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e9c91d5ff25fe81baa34e278a00a69ec60701586","tid":1495391,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟我講！！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我宣布9.13全民大罷工至10.1！」</span></strong